# Map Markers Test - Special Characters

This document tests the rendering of maps with markers that contain special characters.

## Test 1: Single Quotes

<<map type="city" zoom="12">>
center: 37.7749, -122.4194
marker: 37.7749, -122.4194, "Fisherman's Wharf", "San Francisco's most popular tourist destination", "blue"
marker: 37.8024, -122.4058, "Sam's Place", "It's Sam's favorite restaurant", "red"
marker: 37.7955, -122.3937, "O'Reilly's Pub", "The best pub in SF's downtown", "green"
<</map>>

## Test 2: Mixed Quotes (Single and Double)

